---
title: Pappardelle with Rich Fennel Pork Ragu
description: Sometimes you just want to come home and devour a bowl of
comforting pasta. Well, we've taken pasta to a whole new level
with this recipe. Delicious Tuscan pork sausages make for a pretty
tasty sauce, and coupled with our beautiful pappardelle pasta, we
promise you'll be very happy!
